Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "google_access_approval_settings" "<example_resource_name>" {
  project = "<example_resource_id>"

  enrolled_services {
    cloud_product    = "all"       # Critical: enroll all services to enable Access Approval for the project
    enrollment_level = "BLOCK_ALL" # Critical: require approval for all applicable access requests
  }
}
```
